high_descs: Turn around, walk forward, turn to the left to face the counter top
Pick up the egg on the counter top behind the trophy.
Turn around and face the refrigerator, open the refrigerator door
Place the egg inside the refrigerator by the tomato. Close the door, then open the door and pick the egg up.
Turn to the right, walk forward, turn to the right to face the sink.
Place the egg in the sink in front of the white bowl.
anns.task_desc: Pick up the egg, put it in the refrigerator and then put it in the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and stand in front of the toaster.
Pick up the egg to the right of the toaster.
Turn left and go to the fridge.
Chill the egg and pick it up again.
Turn right and then go to the sink on your right.
Put the egg in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold egg in the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and walk forwards before turning left to face the statue
Pick up an egg from off of the kitchen counter
Turn to your left and maneuver to face the fridge
Open the fridge, put the egg in to chill for a few seconds and then take it back out
Turn right and walk into the kitchen until you face the sink
Place the cold egg in the sink
anns.task_desc: Chill an egg and put it in the sink
